query: UPDATE user_settings SET command_style = $2, autopush_option = $3, autopush_duration = COALESCE($4, autopush_duration), autopush_interval_count = COALESCE($5, autopush_interval_count), autopull_option = $6, autopull_duration = COALESCE($7, autopull_duration), autocommit_option = $8, autocommit_duration = COALESCE($9, autocommit_duration), autocommit_interval_count = COALESCE($10, autocommit_interval_count) WHERE user_id = $1
